summary: This document includes a declaration of the custodian of records in response to a Grand Jury Subpoena issued by Assistant United States Attorney Maurene Comey. It certifies the authenticity of records provided in compliance with the subpoena, detailing the nature of the records and their relevance to the ongoing investigation.

persons.name: Maurene Comey
persons.context: Maurene Comey is mentioned as the issuer of the Grand Jury Subpoena requesting records from a business.

persons.name: Lift V.
persons.context: Lift V. is the custodian of records who declares the authenticity of the records provided in response to the subpoena.

events.title: Grand Jury Subpoena Issued
events.description: A Grand Jury Subpoena was issued by Assistant United States Attorney Maurene Comey requesting specific records.

keyFacts: The document is a declaration made under penalty of perjury.
It certifies that the records were made at or near the time of the events they describe.
The declaration is in response to a Grand Jury Subpoena dated September 3, 2019.
The declarant, Lift V., is identified as the custodian of records for a business.
The document outlines the legal standards for the admissibility of the records under Federal Rules of Evidence.
